property.name: org.eclipse.equinox.p2.description
property.value:
XDCtools eclipse-based IDE Client.

This version of XDCtools IDE Client is shared by all projects, independent of the version of the XDCtools Target Runtime Support feature selected via project settings. This XDCtools IDE Client is compatible with the correspondingly versioned XDCtools Target Runtime Support feature as well as all earlier versions of XDCtools Target Runtime Support.

property.value:
XDCtools Target Runtime Support for a Eclipse-based IDEs.

This version of XDCtools Target Runtime Support can be chosen separately for each C/C++ project via its project settings. The correspondingly versioned XDCtools IDE Client, on the other hand, is compatible with this and all earlier releases of the XDCtools Target Runtime Support feature.
